    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis has been properly addressed with rear subframe reinforcement and a VANOS overhaul, ensuring long-term mechanical reliability. It sits on Bilstein B16 dampers for improved transient response and cornering stability. The factory limited-slip differential provides excellent traction out of low-speed bends. While the body shows minor road patina consistent with its mileage, the powertrain remains robust with linear power delivery and a distinct metallic rasp from the quad-exit exhaust. A well-sorted machine for the enthusiast who values analog feedback and mechanical precision.",
      "price": 33500.0,
